ny of Israel as had not known all the wars of Canaan;","year":-1443},{"id":"recrGYNldOTpw93Hi","ref":"Judg.3.2","text":"Only that the generations of the children of Israel might know, to teach them war, at the least such as before knew nothing thereof;","year":-1443},{"id":"recm9UPKlIKccF11B","ref":"Judg.3.3","text":"Namely, five lords of the Philistines, and all the Canaanites, and the Sidonians, and the Hivites that dwelt in mount Lebanon, from mount Baalhermon unto the entering in of Hamath.","year":-1443},{"id":"recs8kR6vBbEGyVvS","ref":"Judg.3.4","text":"And they were to prove Israel by them, to know whether they would hearken unto the commandments of the LORD, which he commanded their fathers by the hand of Moses.","year":-1443},{"id":"recctB5c9w46tioVa","ref":"Judg.3.5","text":"And the children of Israel dwelt among the Canaanites, Hittites, and Amorites, and Perizzites, and Hivites, and Jebusites:","year":-1443},{"id":"rec47plOmNIEUM7sx","ref":"Judg.3.6","text":"And they took their daughters to be their wives, and gave their daughters to their sons, and served their gods.","year":-1443},{"id":"recY3aaNO7G817XIi","ref":"Judg.3.7","text":"And the children of Israel did evil in the sight of the LORD, and forgat the LORD their God, and served Baalim and the groves.","year":-1443},{"id":"recyiK8ucbgIlfsJg","ref":"Judg.3.8","text":"Therefore the anger of the LORD was hot against Israel, and he sold them into the hand of Chushanrishathaim king of Mesopotamia: and the children of Israel served Chushanrishathaim eight years.","year":-1413}]}
